      "amount": "2 cloves",
      "notes": "minced"
    },
    {
      "name": "salt",
      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "black pepper",
      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Cut the halibut fillets into small cubes and place them in a large bowl",
    "Add the thinly sliced onion to the bowl with the fish",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the lime juice, chopped aji amarillo peppers, minced garlic, salt, and black pepper",
    "Pour the lime juice mixture over the fish and onion, making sure that all the fish is coated",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the fish to steam cook in the lime juice",
    "Just before serving, chop the prosciutto into small pieces and add it to the bowl with the fish",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro",
    "Serve the ceviche in small glasses or bowls, garnished with additional cilantro if desired"
  ],
